Package com.example.solocarry.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.solocarry.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<User>
    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<User>
    This is User class that models the User. Each User contains an ArrayList of requests and an ArrayList of friends, it also contains name, email, uid, photoUrl, score.

            java.lang.String photoUrl,
            int score)
        The constructor of a User object. It accepts a name, an email address , an User id, an photo, and a current score, also initializes friends and requests if not exist.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the User
        email - the email address of the User
        uid - the user id of the User
        photoUrl - the photo of the User
        score - the score of the User
